divs: Sighting Detailsyoutubers are finding ufos holographing planes didn't believe it until last night. I live on the flight path of Ohare so I see planes going by my living room window witch faces east. what catches my eyes is that some lights are extra bright so I try and take pictures. last night there was a extra bright light so I grabbed my digital camera, it's set on night so shutter stays open longer and I get a trail of lights. When I reviewed the pictures I was surprised to see that one of the lights had crossed over so it can't be a plane that would be totally impossible. I also happen to catch something flashing by
